				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have a couple questions about modding in Half-Life 1. Please answer me ASAP as I need help greatly.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">1.</span> How do I get my mod to find the map that I set as the starting map in liblist.gam? It keeps saying that it can't find the map on the server. What do I have to do to make the map load and where do I have to put the map so that my mod can find it and start it?
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">2.</span> How do I make the background and logo of my mod's main menu one that I have created and not the default background?
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">3.</span> How do I create a loading point between two maps so that when you walk to a certain point in the first map, you are automatically forwarded to the spawn point in the second map (like in Half-Life).
<br />

<br />
Answers to any of these questions ASAP would be so greatly appreciated! <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /></span><span class=sign></span><span class="gensmall"></span>
