			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Is this for the Steam version of Half-Life 1 or the version that runs without Steam (1.1.1.0)?  If it's the latter, I can help you with the first two:
<br />

<br />
1. Make sure that the gamedir (folder the mod is in) is set correctly in your shortcut.  i.e. +set game gamedir.
<br />

<br />
2. The background is a 256-color 640x480 BMP image named splash.bmp that goes under gfx/shell in the mod's folder: gfx/shell/splash.bmp.  The logo is a .avi file that is 640 pixels wide.  It's named logo.avi and goes under gfx in the mod's folder: gfx/logo.avi.</span><span class=sign></span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by Knightmare on Sun Jul 22, 2007 4:14 pm; edited 1 time in total</span>
                  <br /><br />
                  </td>
			</tr>
