			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">For number three you use a combination of three entities:
<br />

<br />
trigger_changelevel
<br />
trigger_transition
<br />
info_landmark
<br />

<br />
You'll find the entity properties for them here:
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/node/33" target="_blank">http://www.gamedesign.net/node/33</a>
<br />

<br />
and a tutorial on how to use them here:
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.karljones.com/halflife/chnglev.asp" target="_blank">http://www.karljones.com/halflife/chnglev.asp</a></span><span class=sign><br />_________________<br />______________________________________________________</span><span class="gensmall"></span>
                  <br /><br />
