<br />

<br />
A security card is an entity too:
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/node/958#item_security" target="_blank">http://www.gamedesign.net/node/958#item_security</a>
<br />

<br />
read the note at the bottom of that section for tips on how to use the entity to trigger other events.</span><span class=sign><br />_________________<br />______________________________________________________</span><span class="gensmall"></span>
